high_descs: Turn around to the white dining table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn left and go towards the living room, taking the first left past the sofa, then the right into the room.
Slice the loaf of bread in the corner of the room.
Turn towards the shelves next to the room's entrance.
Place the knife on the shelf.
Turn back towards the bread.
Pick up one slice of bread.
Go back towards the dining table you got the knife from, passing it and going into the kitchen, approaching the microwave.
Use the microwave on the slice of bread and remove it.
Walk past the dining table towards the large room, stopping as soon as the wall opens on the left, looking towards the small coffee table just there.
Place the bread on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of bread on a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around to the dining table.
Pick up the knife on the dining table.
Turn left and go toward the sofa, turn into the room next to the sofa.
Slice the loaf of bread beside the pot.
Turn around to the shelf.
Place the knife on the top of the shelf.
Turn around to the bread.
Pick up a slice of the bread from the end closer to you.
Go to the door and turn left, go toward the sofa, then head to the microwave.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave and heat it, then pick it up.
Go to the coffee table across from the sofa
Place the bread on the coffee table behind the pot closer to the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of bread on the coffee table.

high_descs: Head towards to the dining table
Take a knife from the table
Turn to the right
Cut the bread into slices
Head towards to the shelf
Keep the knife inside the shelf
Head towards to the bread
Take a bread from the floor
Head towards to the microwave
Heat the bread take it back
Head towards to the coffee table
Put the bread on the table
anns.task_desc: Take a bread slice put it on the dining table
